 poble atret per la idea del «país dels blancs», un lloc llunyà que alimenta la seva curiositat. Després duna travessia plena dobstacles, arriba a Barcelona i descobreix que la vida allà no és com simaginava. Fins que coneix la Montse, que lacull a la seva família i li ofereix, a més damor i suport, la possibilitat dun futur. LOusman no només laprofita, sinó que la transforma en quelcom molt més gran."},"Planificacions":[{"plan_planificacio":196523,"plan_data":"2026-07-08","plan_sala":"008","plan_sessio":3,"plan_pelicula":4484,"plan_tipuspreu":8,"plan_fila":"17","plan_columna":"15","plan_horainici":"18:00:00","plan_horafi":"19:50:00","plan_numerada":"N","plan_ocupacio":"0","plan_internetbloqueig":"N","plan_fidelitzacioactiva":"S","plan_aforament":"                               LLLLL  LLLLLL LLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLL LLLLL  LLLLLLL        LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLL               ","plan_observacions":null,"plan_ultimamodificacio":null,"plan_article":"","plan_imprimiraforament":"N","plan_dataeliminacio":null,"plan_operarieliminacio":null,"plan_esdeveniment":"N","plan_minutsentradasala":15,"plan_atmbloqueig":"N","plan_taquilllabloqueig":"N","plan_horavall":"S","plan_entradesgratis":"S","plan_estat":"O","plan_aplicarsuplementvip":"S","plan_alacartamovimentinternet":0,"plan_valscampanya":"S"},{"plan_planificacio":196524,"plan_data":"2026-07-08","plan_sala":"008","plan_sessio":5,"plan_pelicula":4484,"plan_tipuspreu":8,"plan_fila":"17","plan_columna":"15","plan_horainici":"20:15:00","plan_horafi":"22:05:00","plan_numerada":"N","plan_ocupacio":"0","plan_internetbloqueig":"N","plan_fidelitzacioactiva":"S","plan_aforament":"                               LLLLL  LLLLLL LLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLL LLLLL  LLLLLLL        LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLL  LLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLLLLL  LLLLLLLLLL